{"tid":722724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長洲致命交通意外","createTime":"2018-06-29T18:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T19:04:31.000Z","uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3819c57edcf3f76440ceba22e6405f8032db6e18","tid":722724,"uid":14454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"警方現正調查今日（六月二十九日）上午在長洲發生的一宗交通意外，意外中一名五十七歲男子死亡。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　上午約十時四十五分，一名五十七歲男子駕駛一輛鄉村車沿長洲體育路往明暉路方向行駛，當駛至近一酒店時，據報鄉村車失控反側。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　司機頭部嚴重受傷，由直昇機送往東區尤德夫人那打素醫院治理，延至晚上十時三十分證實死亡。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　港島總區交通部特別調查隊正跟進調查案件。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　任何人如目睹意外發生或有任何資料提供，請致電三六六○ 六八三八、三六六○  六八四九或三六六○  六八○○與調查人員聯絡。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6858b7e1edb1da273ac3100ddda54b71de032b2","tid":722724,"uid":51272,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"長洲唔係有間醫院咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW R.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd23ad4192d10927de53d23fbb5ed2825395c3ad","tid":722724,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:09:55.000Z","msg":"調去長洲做交警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7290dec69b02d40395b4a854713845d00fd265","tid":722724,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc53807fd44ec562d43ae57e8a0c61e7c10ff37","tid":722724,"uid":41204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:21:36.000Z","msg":"長洲有車？"},{"pid":"d3d0ee4d29a0eb7350e85a44d4fa0642fd3d762c","tid":722724,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dis